nodes.text: Star Wars Look and Find (Journey to Star Wars: The Force Awakens)
Star Wars Look and Find is a Phoenix International Publications Star Wars children's book part of the Journey to Star Wars: The Force Awakens book series. It was published on September 4, 2015.
Travel across the galaxy and explore scenes from the Star Wars saga. Search for more than 100 Star Wars find 'ems, and includes Look and Find scenes and aliens from Star Wars: The Force Awakens.
